      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DREAM ON ALLAN (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 8 lengths at this track in a handy 22.81 beating Somerton Willow. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be right there at the finish again. DR. BENEDICT (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (20.17) at Traralgon. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Leading player again. SAND DUNES (3) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, the latest scoring at Ballarat over 390m. Capable of going well again. IN ONE MOMENT (7) impressed last start, winning in good time. Among the hopes.",
